commit.message:
lots of new options

    0. View queue normally
    1. Remove duplicates from the queue (very useful!)
    2. View with short title info (no longer used)
    3. Change on to True in shortTitle Boolean (no longer used)
    4. Duplicate the first item
    5. Remove the first item
    6. View All Queue info (-csv)
    7. Change email for a request
    8. Move somebody to front of queue (by position)
    9. Find where somebody is in the queue
    10. Duplicate any user in the queue
    11. Move user to the front of the queue
